701415f-a.title: Bronx: Mace Avenue - Barker Avenue
701415f-a.text:
Mace Avenue, at, adjoining and east of the N.E. corner of
Barker Avenue. The two low buildings bear numbers 653 and 655.
The view is from Barker Avenue.
April 3, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
